ML_Workflow.txt includes the full ML workflow checklist:
```
0) Project setup
1) Problem framing
2) Data collection
3) Preprocessing
4) Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
5) Baseline & Models
6) Training & Evaluation
7) Hyperparameter Tuning
8) Packaging & Artifacts
9) Deployment
10) Monitoring & Iteration
```
